org.eclipse.dirigible.database.api

Interface IDatabase

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CustomDatabase, DerbyDatabase, H2Database, ManagedDatabase

    public interface IDatabase
    This interface represents a Database. It allows for querying, modifying and navigating through collections and resources.
